### Health check
GET http://localhost:4000/healthz

### Public root
GET http://localhost:4000/

### Rooms list (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:4000/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Rooms create (idempotent, requires auth)
POST http://localhost:4000/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "room-1"
}

### Submissions — unauthenticated (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:4000/rooms/room-1/submissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": { "msg": "unauth", "ts": "{{$timestamp}}" }
}

### Submissions — authenticated (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:4000/rooms/room-1/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": { "msg": "auth", "ts": "{{$timestamp}}" }
}
